  <releases>
    <release version="2.0.1" date="2026-01-31">
      <description>
        <p>New</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Added ability to export to an editable Annotator file.</li>
          <li>Added support for WebP export.</li>
          <li>Added about window.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Changes</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Updated screenshot to use D-Bus capture mechanism.</li>
          <li>Removed references to gtk3 in build files.</li>
          <li>Improved export menu UI.</li>
          <li>Updated issues with GitHub continuous improvement action.</li>
          <li>Removed Debian packaging files.</li>
        </ul>
