          <li>Added option for transparent PNG export (thanks for Peter Willemsen).</li>
          <li>Added support for adding custom stickers.</li>
          <li>Added support for inserting images.</li>
          <li>Added support for color picker (copy value to clipboard or change current annotation object color).</li>
          <li>Added support for inserting speech and thought bubble shapes.</li>
          <li>Added ability to annotate image by drag/drop on welcome screen.</li>
          <li>Added ability to drag a copy of the annotated image via a new "PNG" icon in the toolbar.</li>
